<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img src="https://www.shongshoy.info/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Screenshot-944-685x1024.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-21339"/></figure></div>
<!-- /wp:image -->

